data.name: textBox2.Text
data.value: At Thread IoT, we specialize in developing cutting-edge utilities tailored to simplify and enhance data exchange across various communication protocols. Whether it's MQTT, TCP, UDP, or Serial communication, our solutions are designed to meet the demands of modern IoT ecosystems and streamline your operations.

data.name: textBox7.Text
data.value: With a strong commitment to quality and innovation, Thread IoT ensures that our solutions are robust, easy to use, and tailored to your needs. Whether you're a developer, an enterprise, or an individual with specific requirements, we’re here to help you achieve your goals with precision and reliability.
